{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/43171", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/43171/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/43171/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/43171/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/43171", "id": 242171371, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyNDIxNzEzNzE=", "number": 43171, "title": "Type system loophole: i32 > 256 converts to u8 converts to char, leading to crash", "user": {"login": "alexispurslane", "id": 1920151, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE5MjAxNTE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1920151?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexispurslane", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2017-07-11T20:20:17Z", "updated_at": "2017-07-11T21:09:17Z", "closed_at": "2017-07-11T21:09:17Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "I have a playground MCVE [here](https://play.rust-lang.org/?gist=6eb52d0f6fa8f43627898e58b8b5e0c7&version=stable&backtrace=0). Essentially, you can case an integer that is over 256, or greater than `char` can represent, to a `u8` and then to a `char`, and get an overflow wraparound, or in my case, for some reason, a crash. My code looks like this in case you don't want to look at the playground:\r\n```rust\r\nfn main () {\r\n    let base: i32 = 255;\r\n    let foo: char = (base + 128) as u8 as char;\r\n    println!(\"{:?}\", foo); // Overflow: `\\u{7f}' (integer value 127)\r\n}\r\n```\r\nI'm not sure if this is intended, it has caused a runtime crash for me so I don't think it is. Hope this helps!", "closed_by": {"login": "alexispurslane", "id": 1920151, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE5MjAxNTE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1920151?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexispurslane", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexispurslane/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/43171/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/43171/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": nul